headline: Accenture (NYSE:ACN) Expands Partnership With OP Financial To Transform Insurance Services
summary: Accenture (NYSE:ACN) recently expanded its partnership with OP Financial Group, enhancing Pohjola Insurance's digital capabilities, further aligning with ongoing tech advancement trends. This collaboration, coupled with Accenture's other initiatives like the AI solution partnership with Dell and NVIDIA, reflects the company's commitment to tech innovation. headline: OP Financial expands tie-up with Accenture to insurance business
summary: Accenture will develop a digital core for Pohjola Insurance by implementing a new cloud-based Guidewire platform for its IT applications.
